HTMLFencedFrameElementConfig.summary: NOTE Experimental The config property of the contains a object, which represents the navigation of a {{htmlelement("fencedframe")}}, i.e. what content will be displayed in it. A FencedFrameConfig is returned from a source such as the Protected Audience API.

remarks.para:
-Fenced frames on developers.google.com
-The Privacy Sandbox on developers.google.com
